<div style="max-width:740px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem">
  <h1 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:0.5rem">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p style="color:#64748b;font-size:0.875rem;margin-bottom:2rem">Effective date: July 1, 2026</p>

  <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1.75">This Privacy Policy describes how NickPicks.com ("NickPicks," "we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and shares information about you when you visit our website at NickPicks.com.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75"><strong>Usage data.</strong> When you visit NickPicks, we automatically collect certain information about your device and how you interact with our site. This includes your IP address, browser type, referring pages, pages visited, and the date and time of your visit. This data is collected through Google Analytics 4 (GA4) and is used in aggregate, anonymized form.</p>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75"><strong>Cookies.</strong> We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to understand how visitors use our site. See the Cookies section below for details.</p>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75"><strong>Contact information.</strong> If you contact us by email, we collect the information you provide in that message (such as your name and email address) solely to respond to your inquiry.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">2. Cookies</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">NickPicks uses the following types of cookies:</p>
  <ul style="margin:0.75rem 0 1rem 1.5rem;line-height:1.75">
    <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — We use Google Analytics 4 to understand aggregate traffic patterns and improve our content. GA4 sets cookies (such as <code>_ga</code>) to distinguish visitors and collect anonymized usage data. Google may transfer this data to its servers in the United States.</li>
    <li><strong>Affiliate tracking cookies</strong> — When you click an affiliate link (such as an Amazon Associates link), the affiliate network may set cookies to track the referral and attribute any resulting purchase to our site.</li>
  </ul>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">Most web browsers allow you to control cookies through browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect some site functionality. You can also opt out of Google Analytics tracking by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">3. Affiliate Links &amp; Third-Party Disclosures</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">NickPicks participates in the <strong>Amazon Services LLC Associates Program</strong> and may participate in other affiliate programs including <strong>Skimlinks</strong>. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may receive a commission — at no additional cost to you.</p>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">Affiliate networks (Amazon, Skimlinks, and others) may independently collect data about your visit via cookies and tracking pixels. Their data collection is governed by their own privacy policies, not this one.</p>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">4. How We Use Information</h2>
  <ul style="margin:0.75rem 0 1rem 1.5rem;line-height:1.75">
    <li>To understand how visitors use our site and improve our content</li>
    <li>To respond to inquiries sent to us by email</li>
    <li>To comply with applicable laws and regulations</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">5. Data Retention</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">Google Analytics data is retained according to Google's standard data retention policy (14 months by default). Email inquiries are retained only as long as necessary to resolve your request.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">6. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">NickPicks is not directed to children under 13 and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us so we can delete it.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">7. Your Rights</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">Depending on your location, you may have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of personal data we hold about you. To make such a request, contact us at <strong>contact@nickpicks.com</strong>.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">8. Links to Third-Party Sites</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">Our site contains links to Amazon.com and other third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites. We encourage you to read their privacy policies.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the effective date at the top of this page. Continued use of NickPicks after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem">10. Contact Us</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.75">For questions about this Privacy Policy or to submit a data request, email us at <strong>contact@nickpicks.com</strong>.</p>

  <p style="color:#64748b;font-size:0.875rem;margin-top:2.5rem">Last updated: July 1, 2026</p>
</div>
